Suggestion: Improve Side Effect Checking\nImprove the side effect checking in the canInlineReferenceDirectly function to correctly identify functions with side effects and check if the corresponding argument is only referenced once. This can be done by modifying the NodeUtil.mayHaveSideEffects and NodeUtil.canBeSideEffected methods to correctly handle functions with side effects.\n
